Use sesame oil during a gallbladder diet, hemp oil helps strengthen immunity.
A good way to increase the supply of beneficial unsaturated fatty acids from these fruits is to use extra virgin oils.
When cold pressed from the seeds, all the healthy substances remain in the oil.
