At least it was idle.
&quot;In the fall, we will disconnect the windmill shaft from the pump in the suction basket again,&quot; explained Mayor Mašek.
Chlum is not the only municipality in the Czech Republic where a windmill has become a municipal emblem, but it is the only village of this type in the entire Vysočina.
