If the Federal Republic of Germany gives an incentive that all migrants from Syria can come to them, the news spreads within hours to all the camps in Europe, but also in Turkey and Jordan.
It encourages another wave of migration to Germany because they simply don&#39;t want to come to us.
We think that the way is to protect the external borders - simply to discourage the waves of migration, help the needy, and separate economic migrants.
Make it clear to them that they don&#39;t stand a chance.
Fifty thousand Kosovars came to Germany last year alone.
From safe Kosovo, where we pay for all the saturation of this state, including the police, courts, prosecutor&#39;s offices.
